font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">Даъвогар: </span><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">{#5}Даъвогарнинг Ф.И.О си</span></p>\n<p class=\"customClass1\" style=\" text-align: right;\"><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">{#6}Даъвогарнинг юридик манзили</span></p>\n<p class=\"customClass1\" style=\" text-align: right;\"><span class=\"structures structure-7\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">{#7}Даъвогарнинг СТИР рақами</span></p>\n<p class=\"customClass1\" style=\" text-align: right;\"><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">{#8}Даъвогарнинг телефон рақами</span></p>\n<p class=\"customClass1\" style=\" text-align: right;\"><span class=\"structures structure-9\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">{#9}Даъвогарнинг электрон манзили</span></p>\n<p class=\"customClass1\" style=\" text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">Жавобгар: </span><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">{#10}Жавобгарнинг Ф.И.О си</span></p>\n<p class=\"customClass1\" style=\" text-align: right;\"><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">{#11}Жавобгарнинг юридик манзили</span></p>\n<p class=\"customClass1\" style=\" text-align: right;\"><span class=\"structures structure-12\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">{#12}Жавобгарнинг СТИР рақами</span></p>\n<p class=\"customClass1\" style=\" text-align: right;\"><span class=\"structures structure-13\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">{#13}Жавобгарнинг телефон рақами</span></p>\n<p class=\"customClass1\" style=\" text-align: right;\"></p>\n<p class=\"customClass1\" style=\" text-align: center; margin-bottom: 22pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">ДАЪВО АРИЗА</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">(</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\">мева-сабзавот маҳсулоти камомади қийматини,</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\">жарима ва зарарни ундириш ҳақида</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">)</span></p>\n<p class=\"customClass1\" style=\" text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px;\"><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Бизнинг манзилга </span><span class=\"structures structure-15\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#15}Тарафлар томонидан тузилган шартнома рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">-рақамли шартномага биноан жавобгар томонидан маҳсулот </span><span class=\"structures structure-16\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#16}Маҳсулотни етказиб бериш усули ( темирйўл, юк машинаси, ҳаво транспорти)</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> орқали </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">етказиб берилди.</span></p>\n<p class=\"customClass1\" style=\" text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px;\"><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Мева-сабзавот маҳсулоти техник жидатдан соз транспортда, бузилмаган тамғалар билан етиб келган.</span></p>\n<p class=\"customClass30\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span>Маҳсулотни миқдори ва сифати бўйича қабул қилиб олиш мобайнида қуйидагилар аниқланди; маҳсулот юк варақаларида кўрсатилганга қараганда камомад билан ҳамда сифатсиз юборилган.</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Бу </span><span class=\"structures structure-17\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#17}Қабул қилиш топшириш давомида тузилган экспертиза хулосасининг рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> рақамли экспертиза далолатномаси, қайта ўлчаш; тижорат далолатномалари ва санитария-эпидемиология маркази хулосаси билан тасдиқланган.</span></p>\n<p class=\"customClass30\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 26.666666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span>Маҳсулотнинг қиймати биз томондан </span><span class=\"structures structure-18\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#18}Маҳсулотнинг қиймати тўланган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> да </span><span class=\"structures structure-19\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#19}Тўлов топшириғи рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> рақамли тўлов топшириғи (тўлов талабномаси, аккредитив) орқали тўланган.</span></p>\n<p class=\"customClass30\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span>Маҳсулот камомади билан келтирилган зарар, мева-сабзавот маҳсулоти сифатсиз юборилганлигидан келтирилган зарар чирик, чиқинди ва йўқотиш харажатлари жами </span><span class=\"structures structure-20\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#20}Даъвогарга етказилган зарарнинг умумий миқдори</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> сўмни ташкил этди.</span></p>\n<p class=\"customClass30\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span>Қайд этиб ўтилган шартномада сифатсиз маҳсулот етказиб берилганлиги учун унинг қийматининг </span><span class=\"structures structure-21\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#21}Шартномага мувофиқ пеня миқдори</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> фоизи миқдорида жарима тўлаш кўзда тутилган, бу эса, юқоридаги суммни ташкил этади.</span></p>\n<p class=\"customClass30\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span>Бизнинг </span><span class=\"structures structure-21\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#21}Шартномага мувофиқ пеня миқдори</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">да юборган <span class=\"leading\"></span>талабномамизни жавобгар (жавобсиз қолдирди), сабабсиз қаноатлантирмади:</span></p>\n<p class=\"customClass30\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span>Юқоридагиларга ҳамда Ўзбекистон Республикаси Фуқаролик кодексининг 437-456-моддалари, Ўзбекистон Республикаси Иқтисодий процессуал кодексининг 148, 149 ва 151-моддаларига асосан</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> </span></p>\n<p class=\"customClass30\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 28px;\"><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">СЎРАЙМАН</span></p>\n<p class=\"customClass30\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 28px;\"></p>\n<p class=\"customClass30\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 28px;\"></p>\n<p class=\"customClass30\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Жавобгардан бизнинг фойдамизга мева-сабзавот маҳсулоти камомади, сифатсиз юборилганлигидан келиб чиққан жарима ва зарар </span><span class=\"structures structure-20\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#20}Даъвогарга етказилган зарарнинг умумий миқдори</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> сўм ундириб беришингизни сўраймиз.</span></p>\n<p class=\"customClass30\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 28px;\"></p>\n<p class=\"consplusnonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-top: 0.75pt; margin-bottom: 0.75pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\">Илова: </span><span class=\"structures structure-23\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\">{#23}Даъво аризага илова қилинаётган ҳужжатлар рўйхати</span></p>\n<p class=\"consplusnonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-top: 0.75pt; margin-bottom: 0.75pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">Даъвогар:</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\">{#5}Даъвогарнинг Ф.И.О си</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\"> ______________</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; font-style: italic;\"> (имзо)</span></p>\n<p class=\"a4\" style=\" margin-top: 0.75pt; margin-bottom: 0.75pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\"> </span></p>\n<p class=\"a4\" style=\" margin-top: 0.75pt; margin-bottom: 0.75pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\">Даъво ариза берилган сана</span></p>\n<p class=\"customClass30\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n</div></div>",
